# 🏢 Real World Scenario

## Situation

An administrator enables UFW on a Linux server.

Users immediately report they cannot connect through SSH.

### Investigation

- Server online ✅
- SSH service running ✅
- Ping successful ✅

### Root Cause

Firewall blocked SSH connections.

### Resolution

Allowed SSH traffic.

```bash
sudo ufw allow ssh
```

Verified firewall rules.

Connection restored.

