# 🎫 Help Desk Ticket

## Issue

Employee cannot remotely access the Linux server.

### Investigation

- Verified network connectivity.
- Confirmed SSH service was active.
- Reviewed firewall configuration.

### Root Cause

Port 22 was not permitted through the firewall.

### Resolution

Allowed SSH service.

Verified successful connection.

Issue resolved.

